The '''Azurite Society of Lords''' was a secret society in the [[New Republic era]]. They were presumably named for the mineral [[azurite]]. The Society was watched by [[Jan Ors]], in her capacity as an agent for [[New Republic Intelligence Service|New Republic Intelligence]]. They were considered an ambiguous threat to the New Republic, comparable to the [[Order of the Canted Circle]].<ref name="UHOTL">''{{Wizards|url=default.asp?x=starwars/article/sw20050407b|series=The Dark Forces Saga|text=Part 2: Unsung Heroes of the Light}}''</ref>

